{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button\/monospacedDigit()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Modifies the fonts of all child views to use fixed-width digits, if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"possible, while leaving other characters proportionally spaced."}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button\/monospaceddigit()"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"monospacedDigit"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A view whose child views’ fonts use fixed-width numeric","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"characters, while leaving other characters proportionally spaced.","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Using fixed-width digits allows you to easily align numbers of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"same size in a table-like arrangement. This feature is also known as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“tabular figures” or “tabular numbers.”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This modifier only affects numeric characters, and leaves all other"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"characters unchanged."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following example shows the effect of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"monospacedDigit()"},{"type":"text","text":" on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"multiple child views. The example consists of two "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" views"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inside an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack"},{"type":"text","text":". Each "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" contains two "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button"},{"type":"text","text":" views, with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the second "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" applying the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"monospacedDigit()"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contents. As a result, the digits in the buttons in the trailing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" are the same width, which in turn gives the buttons equal widths."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["var body: some View {","    HStack(alignment: .top) {","        VStack(alignment: .leading) {","            Button(\"Delete 111 messages\") {}","            Button(\"Delete 222 messages\") {}","        }","        VStack(alignment: .leading) {","            Button(\"Delete 111 messages\") {}","            Button(\"Delete 222 messages\") {}","        }","        .monospacedDigit()","    }","    .padding()","    .navigationTitle(\"monospacedDigit() Child Views\")","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a child view’s base font doesn’t support fixed-width digits, the font"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"remains unchanged."}]}]}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","platforms":[{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS","deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"6.0"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Data\/EnvironmentKeys\/EnvironmentAdditions.swift#L329","fileName":"EnvironmentAdditions.swift"},"title":"monospacedDigit()","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"monospacedDigit"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE15monospacedDigitQryF::SYNTHESIZED::s:11OpenSwiftUI6ButtonV","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Button":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Button","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","role":"symbol","kind"